---
title: Balanced Greek-Style Beef Bowl with Cucumber Freekeh & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Beef and veggies can get a little tiresome, but we bet with this new twist everyone at the table will be wanting a second helping. With flavours of garlic coming from the tender beef strips, a cooling yoghurt dolloped on top of an array of veggies and freekeh, it can be confirmed that beef and veggies are back in the good books!
